---
title: Double BBQ-Glazed Chicken & Loaded Roast Veggie Toss with Corn Chip Crunch & Sour Cream
description: Jazz up juicy chicken bites by coating them in a lip-smacking BBQ sauce, along with our tried and true All-American spice blend.
Serve over a bed of hearty roasted veggies and add the finishing touches with a moreish corn chip crumble for crunch, plus a
dollop of sour cream for some tang.
